terra.shell.modules

Class Module

  • java.lang.Object
    • terra.shell.modules.Module

  • public abstract class Module
extends java.lang.Object
    The Module is an extension of the Shell entirely. A module acts as a daemon run at the start of the Shell, invoked and instantiated by ModuleManagement.class. Modules can be hotloaded using ModuleManagement.hotload(), but this is not recommended unless it is certain not to effect running processes.
    Author:
    dan
